FORCES -- KUWAIT; DIPLOMACY; IRAQ -- FOREIGN POLICY; IRAQ -- FOREIGN RELATIONS 
-- JAPAN; IRAQ -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- EUROPE; IRAQ -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- 
