for Vincent L. Chalk, a high school teacher who died of AIDS Tuesday. Chalk had 
fought the Orange County Department of Education to keep his position as a 
teacher in the program for the hearing-impaired. Dennis Davino, above, signs 
words to the song "Wind Beneath My Wings" during tribute. CHRISTINE COTTER / 
Los Angeles Times; Photo, TRIBUTE TO A HERO: Dennis Davino signs words to the 
