</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
O.C. STOCK WATCH 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Of the 100 largest publicly traded companies in Orange County, 32 gained value 
Thursday, 28 lost and 42 remained unchanged for the day. The following chart 
shows the five biggest percentage winners and losers among county companies' 
stocks. 
</P>
<TABLE CWL="3.21IN:1.78IN:1.89IN" WDM="ABS" NCOLS="3">
<ROWRULE>  </ROWRULE>
<TABLEROW>
<CELLRULE>  </CELLRULE>
<TABLECELL CHJ="C" CVJ="C">
</TABLECELL>
<CELLRULE>  </CELLRULE>
<TABLECELL CHJ="C" CVJ="C">
Thurs. 
</TABLECELL>
<CELLRULE>  </CELLRULE>
<TABLECELL CHJ="C" CVJ="C">
Percent 
</TABLECELL>
<CELLRULE>  </CELLRULE>
</TABLEROW>
<ROWRULE>  </ROWRULE>
<TABLEROW>
<CELLRULE>  </CELLRULE>
<TABLECELL CHJ="C" CVJ="C">
Company 
</TABLECELL>
<CELLRULE>  </CELLRULE>
<TABLECELL CHJ="C" CVJ="C">
